OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA band
OL,6,Fof rain pushes east Friday with
OL,7,Fshowers following later. Bright spells
OL,8,Fand showers on Saturday. Dry and
OL,9,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
